{
  "stem": "14463.4",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was one-- nine months, because we had to have like this-- exit visa from Poland, go through three zones in Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was the British, American, and French.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was not so bad, but we had to get the entrance visa to go through France, which was a hell of a job, because they wouldn't give you a visa to go to Paris unless you had booked something to leave the country within three months, right?",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Either ship or-- you had to have documents, and you have to have tickets to go further, because they didn't want you there, right?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that took nine months.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of those trips I remember very clearly, which was also very tragic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Have I got time to tell you that story now or not yet?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, we'll save it, I think, until the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What date was it when finally you got your visas?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got the visas-- it was somewhere in-- I think it was in April, because in June we left Paris.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In June '47.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Australia, on a ship.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I would like to tell you one little story about--",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
